title: FC#3
body:
As discussed in the discord, in #proposals, we're now to approve or reject the proposal.

The proposal can for FC#3 be seen in: https://jango.me/funding-cycle-3-proposal/

In case of rejection the FC#3 should go on with the same parameters as set for FC#2, which can be seen in: https://juicebox.money/#/p/juicebox

Vote for YES to approve the changes
Vote for NO to keep the current parameters.
